- Restore from `project.config.format` on load (like duration/detail)
- Persist via `patch(/projects/${id}/config, { format })` on change
- Pass to `<RenderSettings format={renderFormat} onFormatChange={...} />`
- Pass to render API call: `post(/projects/${id}/render, { duration, detail, format })`

