## Architecture Flow (Both Paths)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    U["User uploads chapter images"] --> T{"Format Toggle<br/>in RenderSettings"}
    T -->|"📖 Manga"| M1["panelSplitter<br/>gutter detection → 3-4 panels/page"]
    T -->|"📱 Webtoon"| W1["panelSplitter<br/>keep full page → 1 panel/page"]
    
    M1 --> TL["Timeline Builder<br/>maps panels to narration time"]
    W1 --> TL
    
    TL --> R{"Render Loop<br/>per timeline entry"}
    
    R -->|"Manga"| M2["cameraDirector<br/>focus regions prompt"]
    M2 --> M3["generateMultiShotClip<br/>zoom into each region"]
    
    R -->|"Webtoon"| W2["webtoonCamera<br/>scroll analysis prompt"]
    W2 --> W3["buildScrollPath<br/>keyframes with easing"]
    W3 --> W4["buildZoompanExpression<br/>piecewise FFmpeg expr"]
    W4 --> W5["renderScrollClip<br/>single continuous FFmpeg call"]
    
    M3 --> C["Concat → Audio Mix → Subtitles → final.mp4"]
    W5 --> C
```

